116
00:06:59,767 --> 00:07:02,166
And too many still
aren't working at all.

117
00:07:04,233 --> 00:07:10,100
So our job is to
reverse these trends.

118
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:11,433
It won't happen right
away,

119
00:07:11,433 --> 00:07:12,800
and we won't agree on everything.

120
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:17,600
But what I offer tonight
is a set of concrete,

121
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:20,500
practical proposals
